headline: Spotting Winners: Adobe (NASDAQ:ADBE) And Design Software Stocks In Q1
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at Adobe (NASDAQ:ADBE) and the best and worst performers in the design software industry.
